288
00:17:04.042 --> 00:17:06.041
Spider. you're going to live
back in High Camp with Norm.

289
00:17:06.042 --> 00:17:07.791
- What?
- The Windtraders will take you.

290
00:17:07.792 --> 00:17:09.832
- No. Dad.
- No. Dad. He can't.

291
00:17:09.833 --> 00:17:12.332
Spider. you can't live in a mask

292
00:17:12.333 --> 00:17:13.416
day and night.

293
00:17:13.417 --> 00:17:15.332
I just want to stay here with you.

294
00:17:15.333 --> 00:17:18.042
- I know. but it's too risky.
- This isn't fair.

295
00:17:18.875 --> 00:17:21.041
