819
00:45:46.292 --> 00:45:47.374
[Spider] Bro!

820
00:45:47.375 --> 00:45:48.375
[Tuk] Behind us.

821
00:45:50.708 --> 00:45:52.208
- [shouts]
- [Spider hisses]

822
00:45:53.042 --> 00:45:54.667
[Tuk screams]

823
