If I cut now.

845
00:47:18.583 --> 00:47:20.917
do you think Eywa
will come to save him?

846
00:47:22.375 --> 00:47:23.874
Come on. Get these off me.

847
00:47:23.875 --> 00:47:25.249
Come on. They're gonna kill him.

848
00:47:25.250 --> 00:47:26.458
