853
00:47:36.708 --> 00:47:37.708
Come on.

854
00:47:38.417 --> 00:47:39.500
Now give me the knife.

855
00:47:44.333 --> 00:47:45.333
Colonel.

856
00:47:53.667 --> 00:47:54.667
You...

857
