Make it work.

864
00:48:18.292 --> 00:48:20.012
[Lo'ak] I'm telling you. I'm telling you...

865
00:48:20.125 --> 00:48:21.292
there's no thunder.

866
00:48:21.792 --> 00:48:23.125
