- [Jake] Go on.

877
00:48:52.458 --> 00:48:53.458
[snarls]

878
00:48:55.833 --> 00:48:56.874
Stay back.

879
00:48:56.875 --> 00:48:57.958
Get back. Get back.

880
00:49:00.958 --> 00:49:01.999
- Dad.
- Dad.

881
00:49:02.000 --> 00:49:03.291
Sully. we good?

882
00:49:03.292 --> 00:49:05.291
You ready? All right. kids. On me.

883
00:49:05.292 --> 00:49:06.791
All right.

884
00:49:06.792 --> 00:49:08.582
We're gonna ease on outta here.

885
00:49:08.583 --> 00:49:09.707
[sobbing]

886
00:49:09.708 --> 00:49:11.583
- On me. On me.
- [Lo'ak] Keep back.

887
00:49:12.458 --> 00:49:13.458
Keep moving.

888
00:49:17.042 --> 00:49:19.124
- [shouting]
- [gasps]

889
00:49:19.125 --> 00:49:21.458
- [snarls]
- [groaning]

890
00:49:23.792 --> 00:49:25.874
[shouts]

891
00:49:25.875 --> 00:49:26.916
No!

892
00:49:26.917 --> 00:49:27.917
Dad!

893
00:49:30.208 --> 00:49:31.208
[Tuk] Dad!

894
00:49:33.875 --> 00:49:34.957
