895
00:49:34.958 --> 00:49:35.958
Move.

896
00:49:37.208 --> 00:49:39.333
- [Wainfleet grunting]
- [raiders ululating]

897
00:49:45.542 --> 00:49:46.749
- No!
- [Tuk] Dad!

898
00:49:46.750 --> 00:49:48.832
- Dad.
- Dad! Dad!

899
00:49:48.833 --> 00:49:50.833
[breathing heavily]

900
00:49:52.292 --> 00:49:54.875
- [shouts]
- [groaning]

901
00:49:57.417 --> 00:49:59.125
[raiders laughing]

902
00:50:02.208 --> 00:50:03.625
[snarls]

903
00:50:04.917 --> 00:50:06.625
You are strong.

904
00:50:07.333 --> 00:50:09.000
Sky Man.

905
00:50:09.708 --> 00:50:10.708
