953
00:53:51.083 --> 00:53:52.083
[grunts]

954
00:53:52.542 --> 00:53:54.125
- Come on.
- Come on.

955
00:53:54.792 --> 00:53:56.957
- Come on.
- Move it. Move it!

956
00:53:56.958 --> 00:53:59.042
[whooping]

957
