What? Oh.

970
00:54:51.875 --> 00:54:53.332
Easy. easy. Max!

971
00:54:53.333 --> 00:54:55.166
- Be still. child.
- Okay. No. no. no.

972
00:54:55.167 --> 00:54:56.999
No. Stop it. Stop her.

973
