- Daughter.
- My children.

974
00:54:58.375 --> 00:55:00.082
- Neytiri. be calm.
- My children!

975
00:55:00.083 --> 00:55:01.541
Daughter. calm.

976
00:55:01.542 --> 00:55:03.999
My children. The children.

977
